MODIFICATIONS MADE TO ORIGINAL FLORISBOARD:
- Added AI-powered Magic Wand functionality with Gemini API integration
- Enhanced UI with SendRight branding and custom theming
- Implemented auto-close behavior for Magic Wand panel
- Added custom application namespace (com.vishruth.sendright)
- Integrated network permissions for AI API communication
- Modified build configuration for SendRight distribution
- Added custom launcher icons and application identity

